			<b>align</b>: T (Top), TC (Top Center), TR (Top Right), TL (Top Left), C (Center), B (Bottom), BL (Bottom Left), BC (Bottom Center), BR (Bottom Right), LC (Left Center), RC (Right Center), CH (Center Horizontally), CV (Center Vertically).<br>
